But really, Alfred here. After last night's post about holding off on posting Chapter 2 of Contact for story reasons, I realized that I am, in fact, unhealthily obsessed with the world I'm writing.

Fug.

All the signs are flashing and it looks to me like I'm heading down the road to a whole lotta hurt.

Once again, sorry. I said something earlier about having never been so invested in a story, and that turned out to be very true. A little TOO true, if you catch my drift. I'm definitely still writing it, (at this point, I almost can't HELP writing it) I'm just doing it a lot more slowly. Thanks for tuning in, and my sincerest apologies. Catch you next week, deal?
